8. Referential Integrity Rules
  evidence_item.source_id must exist
  citations must reference valid evidence
  promotion_request.artifact_version must match snapshot
9. Migration & Replay Strategy
  schema changes are additive
  historical versions are preserved
  projections rebuilt from events
10. Document Position in DRE Corpus
This data model builds upon:
  NS-DRE-002 — TAXONOMY
  NS-DRE-006 — VERSION
It informs:
  NS-DRE-008 — EEE
  NS-DRE-014 — DATADEF
